properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function strokeWithFootPath() {const thisProp = thisProperty;const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01const lengthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Length Scale').value * 0.01;const p3 = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p3ikfkfreek').transform.position.value;const cw = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Clockwise').value * 0.01;const rotend = thisLayer.effect('Stroke with Foot')('Auto-rotate').value * 0.01;const footrot = thisLayer.effect('Stroke with Foot')('Angle').value;const toetan = thisLayer.effect('Stroke with Foot')('Toe Tangent Angle').value;const heelTan = thisLayer.effect('Stroke with Foot')('Heel Tangent Angle').value;const footA = thisLayer.degreesToRadians((rotend * endctrl.content('Admin').content('ikfkfreekanglessides').transform.anchorPoint[1]) + thisLayer.linear(rotend, 0, 1, (cw > 0 ? 90:270), (cw > 0 ? -90:90)) + (cw > 0 ? footrot : -footrot));const footL = thisLayer.effect('Stroke with Foot')('Length').value * scaleFactor * lengthScale;const tanL = footL * 0.4 // Multiply foot length by a factor to specify tangent lengthconst heelA = cw > 0 ? footA - thisLayer.degreesToRadians(toetan) : footA + thisLayer.degreesToRadians(toetan);const toeA = cw > 0 ? footA - thisLayer.degreesToRadians(180 + heelTan) : footA + thisLayer.degreesToRadians(180 + heelTan);	thisProperty.createPath([p3, thisLayer.add(p3, [Math.sin(footA) * footL, -Math.cos(footA) * footL])], [[0,0], thisLayer.sub(0, [Math.sin(heelA) * tanL, -Math.cos(heelA) * tanL])], [thisLayer.sub(0, [Math.sin(toeA) * tanL, -Math.cos(toeA) * tanL]), [0,0]], false);const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.scale[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                p3,				thisLayer.add(p3, [Math.sin(footA) * footL, -Math.cos(footA) * footL])            ], [[0, 0], [0, 0], [0, 0], [-Math.sin(heelA) * tanL, Math.cos(heelA) * tanL]], [[0, 0], [0, 0], [-Math.sin(toeA) * tanL, Math.cos(toeA) * tanL], [0, 0]], false);        }        else {const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.anchorPoint.value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('curvature').transform.position.value;            return thisProp.createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p1').transform.position.value,                endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('p2ikfkfreek').transform.position.value,                p3,				thisLayer.add(p3, [Math.sin(footA)*footL,-Math.cos(footA)*footL])            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0], [-Math.sin(heelA) * tanL, Math.cos(heelA) * tanL]], [[0, 0], thisLayer.mul(outTangPos, -1), [-Math.sin(toeA) * tanL, Math.cos(toeA) * tanL], [0, 0]], false);        }    }strokeWithFootPath();

properties.name: Stroke Width
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl('ADBE Root Vectors Group')('Admin')('ADBE Vectors Group')('scaleFactor').transform.scale[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;thisProperty.value * scaleFactor * widthScale;
